    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think I've found the source of the problem. The building is locked while the player gives the undeploy order, so [this check](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/bleed/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Traits/Transforms.cs#L74) fails and the order is denied. Normally, `Building::Locked` should be set to false  in `WithMakeAnimation`, but for some reason it never runs. Maybe an error in `Animation::PlayThen`?\n"
